Package src.feedback.enquiry

Class Feedback

java.lang.Object
src.feedback.enquiry.Feedback
Direct Known Subclasses:
Enquiry, Suggestion
public abstract class Feedback extends Object
The Feedback class is an abstract base class for feedback-related objects, such as enquiries and replies. It encapsulates common properties and behaviors for feedback instances, including the description, sender information, and associated camp details.

This class is part of the feedback and enquiry module in the application.
